results.name: Denominators of Blandin-Diaz compositional Bernoulli numbers (B^sin)_3,n.
comment: Numerators are A132092. Numerators and denominators given only for even n (odd n have numerators = 0).
reference: J. Riordan, Combinatorial Identities, Wiley, 1968, p. 199. See Table 3.3.
link: Hector Blandin and Rafael Diaz, Compositional Bernoulli numbers, p. 8, arXiv:0708.0809 [math.CO], 2007-2008.
mathematica: ((x^3)/3!)/(Sin[x]-x) + O[x]^(2m) // CoefficientList[#, x]& // #*Range[0, 2m-2]!& // #[[;; ;; 2]]& // Denominator (* _Jean-François Alcover_, Mar 23 2020 *)
